*{{colorbox|#C20}} Florida (25→27 {{gain}} +2)
*{{colorbox|#C20}} Georgia (13→15 {{gain}} +2)
*{{colorbox|#C20}} Texas (32→34 {{gain}} +2)
*{{colorbox|darkblue}} California (54→55 {{gain}} +1)
*{{colorbox|#C20}} Colorado (8→9 {{gain}} +1)
*{{colorbox|#C20}} North Carolina (14→15 {{gain}} +1)
*{{colorbox|#C20}} Nevada (4→5 {{gain}} +1)
| style="vertical-align:top;" |
*{{colorbox|darkblue}} New York (33→31 {{loss}} -2)
*{{colorbox|darkblue}} Pennsylvania (23→21 {{loss}} -2)
